Register
Steps:
  1) Go to Login https://www.emag.ro/user/login?ref=hdr_signup_btn
  2) Use a new e-mail address example@a.com
  3) Use a valid name, password, password confirmation
  4) Agree to terms
  5) Submit
  
Login
Steps:
  1) Go to Login https://www.emag.ro/user/login?ref=hdr_signup_btn
  2) Use your e-mail address example@a.com
  3) Use the correct password
  4) Submit

Search Valid/Invalid
Steps:
  1) Go to https://www.emag.ro/homepage#opensearch
  2) Type a Valid/Invalid querry
  3) Check results

Add to cart Valid/Invalid
Steps:
  1) Login with an existing user
  2) Type a Valid/Invalid querry
  3) Check results
  4) Select add to cart on the first result
  5) Check cart contents
  
Order
Steps:
  1) Login with an existing user
  2) Type a Valid/Invalid querry
  3) Check results
  4) Select add to cart on the first result
  5) Check cart contents
  6) Proceed to checkout
  7) Select a valid address
  8) Select payment method
  9) Proceed to the next step
Requires a valid test environment with Sandbox payment method

Empty your cart
Steps:
  1) Login with an existing user
  2) Check cart
  3) Delete contents using the already present function
  4) Return to the home page
  5) Check cart contents
  
Add to favorites
Steps:
  1) Login with an existing user
  2) Type a Valid querry
  3) Open the page of the first product
  4) Add to favorites

  
